        "email": "sbuisson@ddn.com",
        "username": "sbuisson"
      },
      "date": "2018-03-01 17:55:28.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nJames, I appreciate your concern about lsvcgss and ARM platform. However, the purpose of this patch is not to address this, but to add an important missing piece when deploying Lustre in a GSS/SharedKeys/Kerberos environment. I hope you can withdraw your -1 review so that this patch can be landed for 2.11. Thanks.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
