      "date": "2018-03-01 23:24:48.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: -Code-Review\n\nI just found a x86 system that cause the same build issues running RHEL7. I can open another ticket but it will collide with this patch.\nAlso I recommend adding your new file to lustre/scripts/Makefile.am as well.",
