      "date": "2018-03-02 09:53:07.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nThanks for pushing separate patch https://review.whamcloud.com/31485 for lsvcgss.\nRegarding lustre/scripts/Makefile.am, I do not catch your point. lgssc.conf is a config file specific to request-key, not a script.",
